The video logs parse as a bit difficult for me to read. I am the type of person who  the articles out loud in my head while I read, so symbols and foreign languages slow me down and compromise my enjoyment.

Having said that, the body horror here is thorough and considerate. Some of the language around the various objects could maybe do with a bit of tightening up but it's not like it's a problem, just an area for possible refinement. Overall, this seems in tune with what I know of and expect from a neo-sarkic jam and liked the rampant body horror enough to give this a safe +1.







